---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import '../styles/global.css';
---

<Base
  title="Privacy Policy — Nexus by AiForStartups"
  description="Privacy policy for Nexus, the operations OS for e-commerce teams."
  canonical="https://aiforstartups.io/privacy/"
>
  <Nav />
  <main class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 pt-32 pb-20">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-sm mb-10" style="color: #8888a0;">Last updated: March 2025</p>

    <div class="space-y-8 text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color: #8888a0;">
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">1. Introduction</h2>
        <p>AiForStartups ("we", "our", "us") operates the Nexus platform. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information when you use our services.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">2. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>We collect information you provide directly (account details, business data), information generated through your use of the platform (order data, customer interactions), and technical data (IP addresses, device information, usage analytics).</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">3. Data Isolation</h2>
        <p>Nexus is a multi-tenant platform. Your organization's data is isolated using PostgreSQL Row-Level Security and is completely invisible to other tenants. We do not share your data with other customers.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">4. Data Security</h2>
        <p>All data is encrypted in transit (TLS) and at rest. We implement industry-standard security practices and conduct regular security reviews.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">5. Contact</h2>
        <p>For privacy-related questions, contact us via <a href="https://wa.me/201040003090" class="text-blue-400 hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">WhatsApp</a> or email at privacy@aiforstartups.io.</p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-xs" style="color: #444458;"><!-- TODO: Complete full privacy policy with legal counsel --></p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Base>
